                    </figure>
                <pb/> 
                    <p>
                        4th example (fig. 17): A stone falls down a steep 
                        mountain slope, rebounding with leaps of increasing 
                        size. A rhythm with rigid articulation.
                    </p>
                    <figure>
                        <graphic url=".../lesson5_fig18"/>
                        <figDesc>
                            5th example: A swimmer's kicks, a rhythm with loose 
                            articulation.
                        </figDesc>
                    </figure>
                    <figure>
