                            An air balloon goes, rising from a warmer into a 
                            cooler layer of air, then again into a warmer layer 
                            and finally into a much warmer layer.
                        </figDesc>
                    </figure>
                    <p>A rhythm with loose articulation.</p>
                <pb/> 
                  <figure>
